gameRecap.title: Game Recap: 76ers 146, Wizards 101
gameRecap.excerpt: The 76ers defeated the Wizards, 146-101. Joel Embiid led the Sixers with his eighth consecutive 30-point game with 34 points, 10 rebounds, and six assists. Tyrese Maxey added 24 points and six assists. Kyle Kuzma led the Wizards with 21 points and nine rebounds. The 76ers have now won three in a row and improve to 15-7 as the Wizards fall to 3-19.
